main event: A witness observed an unidentified object with a dome at the top and a round light shining from within, which moved at high speed without making any sound.
interesting points: The object reflected a bright sheen down behind trees., The sighting occurred in February 1967., The object seemed to move at an estimated 45 degree angle., The witness reported that the object was visually characteristic of familiar phenomena., There was an indication that other similar sightings had occurred in the area.
sighted object: an unidentified flying object with a dome and round light
